<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/61401ATQDMVMSLPDTKCRQGQKNDHQSBBKR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "*AUDITION* Pit Orchestra Class - Hadestown Teen Edition";
  schema:description """
	AUDITION for the NEW Summer Pit Orchestra Class at Old Town Playhouse. This class will include prep for the live orchestra for Young Company's production of Hadestown: Teen Edition, as well as other educational instruction. Performances July 24 and 25. If accepted, tuition of $250 for classes.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Auditions Wednesday, May 27 from 4:30 to 6:30 at OTP. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Classes meet Monday and Wednesday 5pm-7pm, beginning June 15<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Audition materials will be sent out 2 weeks prior to the audition date, along with a more specific time for your audition.<span><br/></span>
""";
