<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "ATP: Heaven on Their Minds";
  schema:description """
	OTP's <a target=\"_top\" href=\"https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/adult-learning/aged-to-perfection.html\">Aged to Perfection</a> group presents two works in staged reading format:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The curtain raiser on the evening, <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Moussaka Meeting</span>, leads you through a warmly touching view of the annual meeting between two sisters.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Next up is <span class=\"ItalicText\">Waiting for God</span>, the outrageously funny tale set at the Bayview Retirement home. An unlikely duo wreak havoc in their refusal to grow old gracefully and to bring everyone else - including families - along for the ride. Forming an unlikely relationship, they scheme to outwit the narcissistic and incompetent manager and his naïve and ever-cheerful assistant. The main characters come together to face the certain realities of aging, and like all classic comedies, it ends with a wedding...well...maybe.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for Informed Audiences due to language.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $10. Please read our <a target=\"_top\" href=\"https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan-your-visit.html\">Plan Your Visit</a> page before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If sold out, please contact the OTP Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-10-17T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/files/1cb683b4-d6b4-42b1-997b-c541d8171303.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/location/407AGBMNMGJMSNPVKJMSNVLRPHJBTDPHT>;
  schema:offers _:4bdb307e74294ec49983d160f745219a6166;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2025-10-17T21:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

