<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/34401AVSCHHTDLGCSLVJRSQLBPTLHDKLB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Beetlejuice JR";
  schema:description """
	The ghost-with-the-most comes to the stage in Beetlejuice JR., the frightfully funny musical based on the beloved motion picture turned Broadway phenomenon. Lydia Deetz is a strange and unusual teenager, still grieving the loss of her mother and obsessed with the whole \"being dead thing.\" Lucky for Lydia, she and her father move to a new house haunted by a recently deceased couple and Beetlejuice, a delightful demon with a real zest for life. When Lydia calls on Beetlejuice to scare away anyone with a pulse, this double-crossing specter shows his true stripes, unleashing a (Nether)world of pandemonium.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performed by students in our Advanced Musical Theatre Workshop.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Note that these performances are at The MATCH, in the Cherryland Mall, 1728 S. Garfield Ave, Traverse City (entrance near the old K-Mart entrance).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for Informed Audiences due to themes of death, relationships, implied intention of suicide, and sexual innuendo.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $22 for Adults, $15 for Youth under 18. Please read our <a target=\"_top\" href=\"https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan-your-visit.html\">Plan Your Visit</a> page before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Performer Families:</span> Complimentary tickets (2 per performer) are available when tuition is paid to the person that paid the tuition. We cannot issue refunds for any tickets purchased, though we can make exchanges.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please call the Box Office for discounted pricing: Groups of 8 or more, Two-on-the-Town card holders, or if you wish to attend with a Service Dog.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If sold out, please contact the OTP Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-07-25T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/files/69ce91b7-fe2e-47a3-99b2-9543b12da87d.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/location/1601APDLPHDNDHQKCQVBHMDTSQVKMKLPQ>;
  schema:offers _:4bdb307e74294ec49983d160f745219a6169;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2025-07-25T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

