html\">Exchange and Refund Policy</a> for options if you cannot use your tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">If sold out</span>, please contact the Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">DRACULA: A COMEDY OF TERRORS</span> is presented by arrangement with Concord Theatricals on behalf of Samuel French, Inc.<span><br/></span>www.concordtheatricals.com<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-30T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
