<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/19201ACDMCRSLDRKDVBCRLQTJMQBCSLCD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Frozen KIDS";
  schema:description """
	Do you want to build a snowman? Join Anna, Elsa, Olaf, Sven, and all your favorite characters as they embark on an epic, ice-filled journey of self-discovery, camaraderie, and the real meaning of true love. This production is sure to prove that \"some people are worth melting for.\"<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performed by our 1-week Musical Theatre Intensive campers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $22 for Adults, $15 for Youth under 18. Please read our <a target=\"_top\" href=\"https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan-your-visit.html\">Plan Your Visit</a> page before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Performer Families:</span> Complimentary tickets (2 per performer) are available when tuition is paid to the person that paid the tuition. We cannot issue refunds for any tickets purchased, though we can make exchanges.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please call the Box Office for discounted pricing: Obstructed View seats, Groups of 8 or more, Two-on-the-Town card holders, or if you wish to attend with a Service Dog.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If sold out, please contact the OTP Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.<span><br/></span>
""";
