<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/49601ASJBNVSCTNMSJHKPCGQLLJSNSJJN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "FUNdraiser - Mismatched Cabaret";
  schema:description """
	Inspired by speakeasy glamour and burlesque flair, this one-of-a-kind cabaret features daring reimaginings of musical theatre favorites, cheeky gender-bending, and performances that lean fully into mature themes. This is musical theatre after dark — irreverent, unapologetic, and delightfully inappropriate.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The night also includes a costume contest, audience interaction, and plenty of opportunities to raise a glass — and join this FUNdraiser for your favorite nonprofit community theatre while you’re at it. Dress for a speakeasy. Come for the mischief. Stay for the cause.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for Mature Audiences due to the adult nature of the show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Doors open one hour before showtime.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is at Hotel Indigo (<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps?daddr=263+W+Grandview+Parkway,+Traverse+City,+MI\">263 W Grandview Pkwy</a>, Traverse City, MI).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Enjoy Early Bird Dinner Specials (4-6PM) at Hotel Indigo's restaurant before <span class=\"ItalicText\">Mismatched Cabaret</span>. A cash bar, special menu with small bites & shareables for purchase, and table service will be available during the show. The perfect dinner-and-a-show night out.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $25, General Admission. No discounts are accepted for this show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If sold out, please contact the OTP Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.
""";
