<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/46801ACDBKCSKJDBSGRJBRPHCJBLCKVCG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "FUNdraiser - Trouble in Deadwood";
  schema:description """
	It's Deadwood, 1876, and Boss Butler wants control of the town. When he makes his move to seize it from the Widow Dawson the town pushes back and there’s a murder! Was it Sawbones the Snake Oil Salesman, the wild woman of a tracker Catastrophe Jones, the outlaw gunslinger Black Bart, or was it Hawkeye Hayes Dawson herself?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Enjoy an evening of mystery and mayhem at Hotel Indigo (<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.google.com/maps?daddr=263+W+Grandview+Parkway,+Traverse+City,+MI\">263 W Grandview Pkwy</a>, Traverse City, MI) while supporting <span class=\"BoldText\">Old Town Playhouse</span> by attending this interactive murder mystery FUNdraiser.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience members are encouraged to dress in their best Wild West attire, with prizes awarded for the best dressed!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">NOTE:</span> Doors open one hour before start time for drinks and appetizers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $85, Reserved Seating (ticket includes appetizers, buffet dinner (<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/userfiles/filemanager/ticqqg59mapniou8dt3e/\">download menu here</a>), dessert, 1 beverage, valet parking, and the show). No discounts are accepted for this show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>If sold out, please contact the OTP Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Trouble In Deadwood</span> is presented under special arrangement with SLEUTHS MYSTERY ENTERTAINMENT.
""";
