<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/16401ABVRRCMPGBBKHVKSLVNQTBRMLVRH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Gala 2025 Sapphire Soirée - Balcony";
  schema:description """
	Join us at the City Opera House for our annual celebratory fundraiser.  This year is a toast to our 65th season with a stunning musical show that celebrates our history and previews our new season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Valet parking available.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>Doors open at 5:30 with Cocktails and Photographer</li><li>6:00 Appetizers and Jewelry Raffle</li><li>7:00 Live Auction, Fund the Season and the Fabulous Gala Show</li><li>9:00 Event Ends</li></ul><span><br/></span>Live auction items include theatre excursions and travel packages.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our <span class=\"ItalicText\">Sapphire Soirée</span> is formal - with a splash of sapphire!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>$75 per person open Balcony seating with appetizers. Includes one drink ticket.
""";
