<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/69401AHRLMSBQLVDQNDHQJHGMBCGHMNBC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Gala 2026 Under the Big Top";
  schema:description """
	Join us at the City Opera House for our annual celebratory fundraiser.  We will have some thrilling performers and a stunning musical show that previews our new season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Valet parking available.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>Doors open at 5:30 with Cocktails, Appetizers, Raffle, and Photographer</li><li>6:30 Dinner, Live Auction, Fund the Season and the Fabulous Gala Show</li><li>9:30 Event Ends</li></ul><span><br/></span>Live auction items include special dinners, travel opportunities, interesting items, and VIP packages.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our <span class=\"ItalicText\">Under the Big Top Gala</span> is formal - join us in Black and White with accents of Red, or as your favorite circus performer!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>$200 per person reserved Ballroom seating with appetizers, dinner, dessert, and open bar. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>When reserving, please let us know if there is anyone else attending that you would like to sit near, and <span class=\"BoldText\">please specify your dinner option</span>:<span><br/></span><ul><li>Beef tenderloin medallions</li><li>Scottish salmon</li><li>Acorn squash, quinoa, and vegetables</li></ul>
""";
