<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/55801ACGDGDJSRRGCLCBTPCSLTJTBNGSM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Hadestown: Teen Edition Tech Class & Crew";
  schema:description """
	For ages 13 to 18. Improve your stagecraft by taking this technical class on Tuesdays & Thursdays, 4:30-6pm, beginning June 16, 2026. The tech class joins the cast rehearsals for tech week and performances July 20-25. Students will learn about the various technical areas - costumes, lights, set, & props - and assist in the creation and running of the production of our Advanced Musical Theater Workshop production.<span><br/></span>If Sold Out, please call the Education Office (231) 947-2210 x102 to be placed on our Waitlist.<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">If registering multiple students, please be sure to fill out name and emergency information for additional students in the box provided at checkout.</span>
""";
