<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/77201ACHJGSDMKVSDQSJLPVNTKPPQRMCG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Honky Tonk Laundry";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Written by Roger Bean</h2><h2>Music Arrangements by Jon Newton</h2>Move over, Thelma and Louise! When Lana Mae Hopkins, owner and proprietress of the Wishy Washy Washateria, hires Katie to help out in the laundromat, they soon find themselves up to their elbows in soap, suds, and cheatin’ hearts. These two country angels join forces to turn their good ol’ laundromat into a bootscootin’ honky-tonk and exact a touch of revenge against those that done ‘em wrong, all while guaranteeing every customer a good, clean time!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Directed by Delynda Moravec and Deb Jackson</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Tickets:</span> Tickets are $44 for Adults, $30 for Youth under 18. No other discounts are accepted. Please contact the Box Office if you wish to attend with a Service Dog. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Content Guidance:</span> You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/content-guidance.html\"> Informed Audiences</a> due to some sexual references, profanity, and depictions of prescription drug and alcohol use.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Attending a Performance:</span> We recommend that you review our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/\">Plan Your Visit</a> pages before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">No refunds;</span> exchanges are often possible. See our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/exchange-and-refund-policy.html\">Exchange and Refund Policy</a> for options if you cannot use your tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">If sold out</span>, please contact the Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">HONKY TONK LAUNDRY</span> is presented by arrangement with Concord Theatricals.<span><br/></span>www.concordtheatricals.com<span><br/></span>
""";
