<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/72401ALBRMBPTSKCJBKRLLGDCPJPQJQDT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Next Fall";
  schema:description """
	<h2>by Geoffrey Nauffts</h2>A witty and provocative look at faith, commitment and unconditional love. While the play's central story focuses on the five-year relationship between Adam and Luke, Next Fall goes beyond a typical love story. Luke is devoutly religious and Adam, an atheist. This timely and compelling play forces us all to examine what it means to \"believe\" and what it might cost us not to.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Directed by Terri Heffron</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Tickets:</span> Tickets are $25. Please contact the Box Office if you wish to attend with a Service Dog. Discounted pricing is available for groups of 8 or more, Two-on-the-Town card holders, Military or Students with ID <span class=\"ItalicText\">only</span> by contacting the Box Office.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Content Guidance:</span> You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/content-guidance.html\"> Informed Audiences</a> due to language and themes of LGBTQ+ experiences.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Attending a Performance:</span> We recommend that you review our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/\">Plan Your Visit</a> pages before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">No refunds;</span> exchanges are often possible. See our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/exchange-and-refund-policy.html\">Exchange and Refund Policy</a> for options if you cannot use your tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">If sold out</span>, please contact the Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">NEXT FALL</span> is presented by arrangement with Concord Theatricals on behalf of Dramatists Play Service.<span><br/></span>www.concordtheatricals.com
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-11-06T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
