<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/40201AJMHGMLBHTGVNKHNPGVSVHHPSMBQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sandbox at Old Town Playhouse";
  schema:description """
	<h2>A monthly acting workshop for actors, by actors.</h2>Honing your skills as an actor and doing it with creative friends is the best way to grow your love of acting and get you more comfortable making strong choices both at auditions and in shows. Sandbox is the place where adult actors can try new characters, work their favorite scenes with friends and fellow actors, or if you’re a writer, bring your scene to workshop with actors! The more we get to \"play in the sandbox\", the more we fuel our love of the art! No experience necessary. Limit is 16 actors per Sandbox session. No charge, but registration is required.
""";
