<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/60601ATNTMJGPJLLKLVBRSMHPPDCNKPMC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Spring Class Showcase 2026";
  schema:description """
	Spring Class Showcase featuring Children of Lir and Willy Wonka KIDS. Children of Lir is a brand new take on a classic Irish folk tale, adapted by Deni Don Hunting. Willy Wonka KIDS transports you to a \"World of Pure Imagination\". Performs May 19, 6:00pm at the City Opera House, downtown Traverse City.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets only available for purchase through accounts under which class tuition was paid. Please log in with this account to proceed. If you have questions, please contact the Box Office. 
""";
