<http://www.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/event/39602ADJGBBDTSCHMNLJTKBSQMMMGMGHD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Ten November";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Dinner Theatre at the Grand Traverse Yacht Club</h2><span><br/></span>Ten November is a dramatic play that recounts the true story of the SS Edmund Fitzgerald, a Great Lakes freighter that tragically sank during a fierce storm in November 1975. Through haunting monologues, songs, and vivid storytelling, the play honors the lives lost and explores the enduring mystery and emotional impact of the disaster.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Book by Steven Dietz<span><br/></span>Music and Lyrics by Eric Peltoniemi</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Directed by Michelle Dungjen</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for General Audiences with some mild language.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Attending This Show</span><span><br/></span>Performances at the <span class=\"BoldText\">Grand Traverse Yacht Club</span>, 13615 S West Bay Shore Dr., Traverse City. Doors open at 5:45 PM for dinner. The performance begins at 7:00 PM.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are $75 reserved seating includes dinner buffet. No other discounts, OTP complimentary tickets, or OTP complimentary gift certificates may be used for this production.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Friday, November 7, performance is for Yacht Club Members only. Please contact the Yacht Club for tickets.<span><br/></span>Satuday, November 8 and Sunday November 9 performance tickets available through the OTP Box Office or website.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>No refunds; exchanges often possible more than 24 hours before a performance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Dinner Menu</span><span><br/></span><ul><li>Arancini (fried risotto cheese balls) with House Marinara</li><li>Honey Glazed Organic Carrots, Roasted </li><li>Chicken Piccata with White Wine Caper Sauce (Vegan Breaded Eggplant available on request, <span class=\"BoldText\">please indicate number of Vegetarian tickets on checkout</span>)</li><li>Caesar Salad with Shaved Parmesan and Hand Torn Crouton </li></ul><span><br/></span>TEN NOVEMBER is presented by arrangement with Concord Theatricals. www.concordtheatricals.com<span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2025-11-08T17:45:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/files/4b5cf10f-ab30-49ef-9021-dc4a06a3b80b.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/oldtownplayhouse/location/1801APGQPRKNVLCHGSKJBCTJKDRMGPLNL>;
  schema:offers _:4bdb307e74294ec49983d160f745219a6316;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2025-11-08T19:15:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

