  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Sound Inside";
  schema:description """
	<h2>by Adam Rapp</h2>Writing professor Bella Baird stands before the audience, ready to tell her latest story, but not everything is as it seems - not every detail fits together. When she meets a surprising new student, their fateful encounter threatens to upend Bella's quiet, everyday life. \"The Sound Inside\" takes twists and turns that will remind you that everyone is writing their own story - but is everyone a reliable narrator?<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Directed by Nancy Sheeber</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Tickets:</span> Tickets are $25. Please contact the Box Office if you wish to attend with a Service Dog. Discounted pricing is available for groups of 8 or more, Two-on-the-Town card holders, Military or Students with ID <span class=\"ItalicText\">only</span> by contacting the Box Office.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Content Guidance:</span> You are the best judge of what is appropriate for those you bring to the theatre, but OTP recommends this show for <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/content-guidance.html\"> Informed Audiences</a> due to discussions of self-harm, sexual content.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Attending a Performance:</span> We recommend that you review our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/\">Plan Your Visit</a> pages before purchasing tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">No refunds;</span> exchanges are often possible. See our <a target=\"_top\" href=\" https://www.oldtownplayhouse.com/performances/plan/exchange-and-refund-policy.html\">Exchange and Refund Policy</a> for options if you cannot use your tickets.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">If sold out</span>, please contact the Box Office to be added to the waiting list.<span><br/></span>
""";
